To build the Eclipse plugin, install the Eclipse Plug-in Development
Environment (PDE), then execute:

	ant -Declipse.home=<path to eclipse> build-all-plugins generate-update-site

Add local update site to Eclipse:

	file:<path prefix>/Tools/ABS/trunk/eclipse-plugin/update-site

Note that the Apet and Costabs (SACO) plugins only run on Linux.

Deploy remote update site (needs access to the server):

	ant -Declipse.home=<path to eclipse> deploy-update-site
